ean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State.inlineHandledInvariants\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">State</span>.<span class=\"name\">inlineHandledInvariants</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State\">State</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashSet/Basic.html#Std.HashSet\">Std.HashSet</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Set of invariant numbers that have been inline-elaborated by `Driver.emitVC` via\n`tryInlineInvariant`. The post-hoc invariant elaboration in `Frontend` consults\nthis to know which user-provided alts have already been consumed (so it doesn't\nwarn about them). ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State.inlineHandledInvariants","kind":"def","line":169,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State.inlineHandledInvariants","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.lean#L169-L169"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State.fuel\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">State</span>.<span class=\"name\">fuel</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State\">State</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/VCGen/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Fuel\">Fuel</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Remaining VC-generation steps. Initialized from `Context.config.stepLimit` (or\n`.unlimited` when no limit is set). Decremented at each successful program-shape\nstep (`tryLetHoist`, `trySplit`, `tryFvarZeta`, `applySpec`). When exhausted,\n`solve` short-circuits and emits the current goal as a VC.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State.fuel","kind":"def","line":163,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State.fuel","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.lean#L163-L163"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State.simpState\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">State</span>.<span class=\"name\">simpState</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.State\">State</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/SimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.State\">Meta.Sym.Simp.State</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Persistent cache for the `Sym.Si